flowchart TD
    Start([Start Loop]) --> FindOne1[1. find_one: Check Data]
    FindOne1 --> DataExists1{Data Exists?}

    DataExists1 -- Yes --> ReturnData1([Return Data])
    DataExists1 -- No --> SetLock[2. find_one_and_update: Try Set Lock]

    SetLock --> LockedByMe{Got Lock?}

    %% Path if we did NOT get lock
    LockedByMe -- No --> FindOne2[3. find_one: Check Data Again]
    FindOne2 --> DataExists2{Data Exists?}
    DataExists2 -- Yes --> ReturnData2([Return Data])
    DataExists2 -- No --> ContinueLoop[Continue Loop]
    ContinueLoop --> Start

    %% Path if we DID get lock
    LockedByMe -- Yes --> Generate[Generate Phrase & Style]
    Generate --> UpdateAndUnlock[4. find_one_and_update: Save Data & Unlock]
    UpdateAndUnlock --> ReturnGenerated([Return Generated Data])

    %% Exception Handling
    SetLock -.-> Exception{Exception?}
    Generate -.-> Exception
    UpdateAndUnlock -.-> Exception

    Exception -- Yes --> ResetLock[5. find_one_and_update: Reset Lock]
    ResetLock --> ContinueLoop